{"sha": "198030fadfbc3849f004deb8bb9108d0a0fad19a", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjE5ODAzMGZhZGZiYzM4NDlmMDA0ZGViOGJiOTEwOGQwYTBmYWQxOWE=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Alex Crichton", "email": "alex@alexcrichton.com", "date": "2014-09-03T01:39:19Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Alex Crichton", "email": "alex@alexcrichton.com", "date": "2014-09-08T19:54:32Z"}, "message": "std: Turn down the stdout chunk size\n\nI've found that 64k is still too much and continue to see the errors as reported\nin #14940. I've locally found that 32k fails, and 24k succeeds, so I've trimmed\nthe size down to 8192 which libuv happens to use as well.\n\nIt sounds like the limit can still be hit with many threads in play, but I have\nyet to reproduce this, so I figure we can wait until that's hit (if it's\npossible) and then take action.", "tree": {"sha": "17b7abcce3660d7ed29dbed9e968c923ef64bffd", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/17b7abcce3660d7ed29dbed9e968c923ef64bffd"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/198030fadfbc3849f004deb8bb9108d0a0fad19a", "comment_count": 13, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/198030fadfbc3849f004deb8bb9108d0a0fad19a", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/198030fadfbc3849f004deb8bb9108d0a0fad19a", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/198030fadfbc3849f004deb8bb9108d0a0fad19a/comments", "author": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/us